---
---
<section class="testimonials-section" aria-labelledby="testimonials-heading">
  <div class="testimonials-inner">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">What teams say</div>
      <h2 id="testimonials-heading" class="section-title">Loved by product teams.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="cards-grid">
      <figure class="testimonial-card reveal delay-1" role="article">
        <div class="card-stars" aria-label="5 stars" role="img">
          <svg width="80" height="14" viewBox="0 0 80 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M7 1l1.75 5.5H14L9.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L7 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L0 6.5h5.25L7 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M23 1l1.75 5.5H30L25.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L23 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L16 6.5h5.25L23 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M39 1l1.75 5.5H46L41.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L39 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L32 6.5h5.25L39 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M55 1l1.75 5.5H62L57.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L55 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L48 6.5h5.25L55 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M71 1l1.75 5.5H78L73.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L71 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L64 6.5h5.25L71 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="card-quote">
          "Nebula replaced three tools and a full-time analyst. We ask questions we'd never have bothered to query before."
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="card-author">
          <div class="author-avatar" aria-hidden="true">MC</div>
          <div>
            <div class="author-name">Maya Chen</div>
            <div class="author-role">VP Product, Vertex</div>
          </div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="testimonial-card reveal delay-2" role="article">
        <div class="card-stars" aria-label="5 stars" role="img">
          <svg width="80" height="14" viewBox="0 0 80 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M7 1l1.75 5.5H14L9.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L7 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L0 6.5h5.25L7 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M23 1l1.75 5.5H30L25.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L23 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L16 6.5h5.25L23 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M39 1l1.75 5.5H46L41.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L39 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L32 6.5h5.25L39 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M55 1l1.75 5.5H62L57.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L55 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L48 6.5h5.25L55 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M71 1l1.75 5.5H78L73.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L71 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L64 6.5h5.25L71 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="card-quote">
          "First analytics tool our whole team actually opens. The plain-English queries are magic."
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="card-author">
          <div class="author-avatar av-2" aria-hidden="true">DA</div>
          <div>
            <div class="author-name">Diego Alvarez</div>
            <div class="author-role">Head of Growth, Loop</div>
          </div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="testimonial-card reveal delay-3" role="article">
        <div class="card-stars" aria-label="5 stars" role="img">
          <svg width="80" height="14" viewBox="0 0 80 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M7 1l1.75 5.5H14L9.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L7 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L0 6.5h5.25L7 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M23 1l1.75 5.5H30L25.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L23 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L16 6.5h5.25L23 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M39 1l1.75 5.5H46L41.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L39 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L32 6.5h5.25L39 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M55 1l1.75 5.5H62L57.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L55 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L48 6.5h5.25L55 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
            <path d="M71 1l1.75 5.5H78L73.5 9.75l1.75 5.5L71 12l-4.25 3.25 1.75-5.5L64 6.5h5.25L71 1z" fill="#a855f7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="card-quote">
          "We caught a churn spike days earlier than we would have. That alert paid for the year."
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="card-author">
          <div class="author-avatar av-3" aria-hidden="true">PN</div>
          <div>
            <div class="author-name">Priya Nair</div>
            <div class="author-role">PM, Cirrus</div>
          </div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials-section {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--bg-2) 50%, var(--bg) 100%);
  }

  .testimonials-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--pink);
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.2);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cards-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .testimonial-card::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 6rem;
    line-height: 1;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @media (hover: hover) {
    .testimonial-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.07);
    }
  }

  .card-stars {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .card-quote {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .card-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6);
    color: white;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .author-avatar.av-2 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #ec4899);
  }

  .author-avatar.av-3 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22d3ee, #6366f1);
  }

  .author-name {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .author-role {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--muted-2);
  }
</style>
